Dear friends, just because it’s the opening of  @arianaspersiankitchen doesn’t mean I have forgotten about my country my people my motherland. The hardship the injustice the genocide  hasn’t been forgotten. 
My stories now are mostly about my restaurant but my place represents the new Iran we all want and deserve: colorful, happy, bright, inviting and most importantly female led. If you’re in Dubai please come and immerse yourself in your beautiful culture
 #zanzendegiazadi #mahsaamini #iranrevolution #freeiran #freedomofchoice 💚🤍❤️

Norouz Pirooz 1402 to all my beautiful friends followers & family, freedom is around the corner I can feel it. Pls keep thinking positive, let’s manifest the Iran we want and see it come to life. We are thinking about all the people who are suffering during this ‘festive’ season. Our thoughts & prayers are with you. #zanzendegiazadi #womanlifefreedom #freeiran #freedomofchoice ✊🏼🕊️🌸

My Persian Feta cheese board w creamy LIGHVAN  cheese, chopped fresh Sabzi Khordan ( fresh tarragon, basil, mint) dried mint, activated walnuts served with our 72 hours fermented Barbari bread. Easy modern pretty and yummy take on the way we all normally serve it.  WOW ✨
Best of all you can eat it at @arianaspersiankitchen under majestic Kashani domes located in the hottest hotel in the world @atlantistheroyal 🔥
Or make it easily at home 😋
ps Happy to finally be filming in my dream kitchen 🤩
@arianabundy 
#teamAPK 🙌🏼
Excuse my (clean) sleeves 🙈

“Dear friends, I’ve decided to remove my last post out of the fact that some of you who don’t know my work seemed genuinely hurt and disillusioned by the fact that I wore a Hejab (albeit a very loose one) in order to be able to visit the famous Golestan factory. My aim was to promote Persian food products and women owned businesses. 
The last thing I would want is for us to lose hope and be divided. Thanks for the wake up call ✊🏼💗✊🏼💗

✨Let me transport you to Anzali bazaar where you can find the freshest most beautiful seasonal produce. The soil sun and water of this incredible land of Iran by the Caspian Sea grows fruits & veg which one you taste will forever be imbedded  in your mind ✨

What an honor to have His Highness Sheikh Mohammad bin Rashid Al Maktoum @hhshkmohd dine with us @arianaspersiankitchen ✨🙏🏼✨

His grace & generosity back in 2016 was the reason this restaurant was even created! I was given Carte Blanche to dream big and showcase our incredible Persian cuisine and culture in a whole new way. 
With the help of a stellar team at  @atlantistheroyal #Kerzner and design help from #GAdesignlondon @bass_interior_design…and 6 long years…we were able to create magic @atlantistheroyal ✨

Thank you your Highness for your kindness, vision and for making us all feel at home in your country….where anything is truly possible ✨
@michelinguide #michelinrestaurant
